version_description: To play along with the CD Dire Straits version, you will need to tune down one semitone. I have stuck to simple chords that fit well with the original recording.
Well-aligned chords for all parts of the song / tabs for links.

Basic chords play with clean electric guitar with Slapback effect ,originaly recorded around the "Brothers In Arms" sessions 1983 and used in the US as a B side to "So Far Away".https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lkG6VTS7q-E.
Complete version,play acoustic guitar or Clean Electric with Vhorus/Reverb effects. https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BlD6jCGVU4A.
Simpler key for acoustic/capo version -matches original uncapoed.
